---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CallButton from '../components/CallButton.astro';

const siteUrl = 'https://windshieldreplacementlubbock.com';
---

<Layout
  title="Mobile Windshield Repair Lubbock TX | We Come to You"
  description="Mobile windshield replacement & repair service in Lubbock, TX. We come to your home, office, or anywhere. Call (806) 450-8900 for same-day service."
  canonical={`${siteUrl}/mobile-service`}
>
  <Header />

  <section style="background-color: #1e3a8a;" class="text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">Mobile Windshield Service in Lubbock, TX</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg max-w-2xl">We bring the shop to you. Full windshield replacement and chip repair done at your location — home, office, parking lot, wherever you are in Lubbock.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <CallButton label="Call Now — We Come to You: (806) 450-8900" size="md" />
    </div>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">No Shop Visit Required</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Most auto glass shops expect you to drive a damaged vehicle across town, sit in a waiting room for an hour, and hope your schedule can accommodate their hours. We do things differently. Our mobile windshield service brings everything needed for a full replacement or chip repair directly to you — at your home, your workplace, your apartment complex near Texas Tech, or anywhere else in the Lubbock area.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The quality of a mobile installation is identical to a shop installation. We carry the same professional equipment, the same quality glass, and use the same installation techniques whether we're in your driveway off 50th Street or in a parking lot on 82nd Street. Mobile just means more convenient for you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        For most vehicles, all we need is a reasonably flat, sheltered surface — a garage or carport is ideal, but a regular driveway or parking spot works fine in most conditions. We'll let you know if there are any requirements when you call.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Popular Mobile Service Locations in Lubbock</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        We've done mobile service all over Lubbock. Here are some of the most common locations we service:
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Residential Neighborhoods</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Home service in Tech Terrace, Heart of Lubbock, Maxey Park, South Overton, North Overton, Arnett Benson, Clapp Park, Stubbs-Stewart, Bayless-Atkins, Wheelock, Monterey, and every other neighborhood in Lubbock. We pull up in your driveway and you can stay inside the house while we work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Office Parking Lots</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Many of our customers are busy professionals who can't afford to leave work to sit in a shop. We'll come to your office, fix your windshield in the parking lot while you're at your desk, and text you when we're done. Your workday doesn't need to be interrupted at all.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Texas Tech University Area</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We serve the University Avenue corridor, campus-adjacent apartment complexes, and the surrounding residential streets constantly. Texas Tech students and faculty are among our most frequent customers — gravel, hail, and tight budgets are all common concerns we're well-equipped to handle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Airport &amp; Industrial Areas</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Workers at Lubbock Preston Smith International Airport and the surrounding industrial and logistics facilities on the south side of town use our mobile service regularly. We work around shift schedules and come to you on your time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">South Plains Mall Area</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">The Loop 289 and South Plains Mall corridor is one of the busiest commercial areas in Lubbock. If you're shopping, working, or just parked in the area, we can meet you there and take care of your windshield while you go about your errands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Surrounding Towns</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We regularly provide mobile service to Wolfforth, Shallowater, Idalou, Ransom Canyon, Slaton, New Deal, and Abernathy. If you're outside Lubbock proper, call us and we'll confirm we can reach you — most of the time we can.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">What to Expect With Mobile Service</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg min-w-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">1.</span>
          <div><strong>You call us</strong> and describe your vehicle and the damage. We give you a quote and check your insurance coverage on the spot.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg min-w-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">2.</span>
          <div><strong>We schedule a time</strong> that works for you — same-day whenever possible. We'll also confirm your location.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg min-w-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">3.</span>
          <div><strong>Our tech arrives</strong> with all equipment and your replacement glass. We'll text or call when we're on the way.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg min-w-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">4.</span>
          <div><strong>We complete the job</strong> — usually 60–90 minutes for a replacement, 30 minutes or less for a chip repair. You don't need to be present; just make sure the vehicle is unlocked if we need to run recalibration.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg min-w-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">5.</span>
          <div><strong>Done.</strong> We'll give you safe drive-away instructions and clean up any glass debris from the area. Your day can continue as planned.</div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">24/7 Emergency Mobile Service</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Sometimes windshield damage happens at the worst possible time. A late-night crack, a hailstorm at 2am that leaves your vehicle exposed, an early morning discovery before a long drive. We offer 24/7 emergency mobile service for situations where you can't wait until a shop opens at 8am.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        If your windshield is shattered and your vehicle is at risk — whether from weather exposure or you simply can't safely drive it — call us any time. We'll get someone out to you as quickly as possible.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center py-10 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Book Your Mobile Appointment</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 max-w-xl mx-auto">Tell us where you are in Lubbock and when works for you. We'll take care of the rest — including your insurance if you have comprehensive coverage.</p>
      <CallButton label="Call (806) 450-8900 — We Come to You" size="lg" center={true} />
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">Same-day appointments available &bull; 24/7 emergency service</p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
